​
Welcome to Corks
​
​
Corks is your bar!  ​We are a family owned hometown pub located in Historic Downtown Bradenton where everyone knows your name and where you feel like family once you sit down.  Cork and Susan Miller have owned Cork's for 10 plus years and considers all that come in family.  We proudly support our Crew of Hernando Desoto and many other local organizations.  Cork's is a relaxed style pub where you can enjoy a great happy hour or order a top shelf bourbon.  Thank you for stopping by and being apart of the Cork's Family!
A Little Sneak Peek
Whiskeys: Eagle Rare, Blantons, Buffalo Trace, Woodford Distillery, Four Roses Distillery, Old Forester Distillery, Chicken Cock, Yellowstone, Bookers, Widow Jane, Garrison Brothers, Short Barrel, Makers, Jameson, Tullamore Dew, Fox & Oden, Peerless, Whistle Pig, Makers, Jim Beam, Basil Hayden Bourbons, Elijah Craig, Jefferson Reserve, Blue Run, Gentleman Jack and Jack Daniels, Michters, Angels Envy & Rye, Bulleit Bourbon & Rye, Uncle Nearest, 1792 and more.
Wine: House Wines on Happy Hour till 7pm for $4. We also carry Juggernaut Cabernet & Pino Noir, Carnivor Cabernet, Apothic Blend, Four Vines Zinfindel, Josh Merlot, Meiomi Pino Noir, Lola Pino Noir & Chardonnay, Squealing Pig Sauvignon Blanc, Hess Chardonnay, Relax Reisling, Prosecco, Brut. We also carry a Non Alcoholic Brut.
Beers: We have on draft Bud Light, Miller Lite, Shock Top, Mango Cart, Paulaner Hefe, Kona Big Wave, Night Swim Porter, Cigar City Jai Alai, Yuengling, Florida Avenue Blueberry Wheat, Stella Artois, Guinness, Rotating Ciders & Seasonal Beers. Bottles include domestics, some Florida Brews and imports like Corona, Heineken.  N/A Bud Zero, Clausthaler & Heineken Zero.
Cigars: We carry a selection of 40 cigars including Monte Cristo, Cohiba, Perdomo, Oliva, Macanudo, Acid, Leaf by Oscar, Islan Jims, My Father, Leather Rose, Rocky Patel and we are always rotating cigars.  Feel free to bring your own or try one of ours.  We have all the utensils for you to use while enjoying a cigar at Cork's and if you like we sell Cigar Lighters and Cutters to t
ake with you.
